          41.8359375,
          650.1650390625
        ]
      ],
      "text": "Xanthones are natural, semisynthetic and totally synthetic heterocyclic compounds with the dibenzo-g-pyrone framework. Xanthone molecules having a variety of substituents on the different carbons of the nucleus constitute a group of compounds with a broad spectrum of",
      "section_hierarchy": {
        "2": "/page/0/SectionHeader/15"
      }
    },
